      "description": "Affordable opportunity for the right buyer. This vehicle is being offered as a straightforward, budget-conscious option with clear value for someone looking for basic transportation, a project, or a parts candidate. It presents as a practical purchase at an accessible price point, with plenty of upside for an owner willing to put in a little work. Priced to sell and represented honestly.",
