    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left in it? This car is a great budget-friendly option for someone who wants basic transportation or a solid little project to tinker with. It\u2019s not perfect, but it\u2019s got character, and at this price it could be a smart buy for the right person. If you want something inexpensive and straightforward, come take a look \u2014 I\u2019m happy to answer questions and be upfront about it.",
      "price": 6900.0,
