      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough, honest driver with solid project potential. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the transmission engages as it should, and it has the kind of mechanical character that makes it a worthwhile fixer for someone who appreciates a hands-on car. Cosmetically it shows its age and will need attention, but the fundamentals are there for a dependable budget commuter, shop runabout, or weekend restoration candidate. If you want an inexpensive entry point with usable bones and plenty of upside, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
